Come out of that water at once!

01:11:35.083 --> 01:11:37.501
Oh. You must be Baroness Schraeder.

01:11:43.007 --> 01:11:45.258
Oh, I'm soaked to the skin!

01:11:46.260 --> 01:11:50.180
