♪ Every song that it hears ♪

01:15:18.598 --> 01:15:20.974
♪ My heart wants to beat ♪

01:15:21.058 --> 01:15:24.269
♪ Like the wings of the birds that rise ♪

01:15:24.353 --> 01:15:27.397
♪ From the lake to the trees ♪

