02:11:57.326 --> 02:12:04.332
♪ Perhaps I had a miserable youth ♪

02:12:04.417 --> 02:12:10.922
♪ But somewhere in my wicked, miserable past ♪

02:12:11.007 --> 02:12:17.554
♪ There must have been a moment of truth ♪

