02:13:26.540 --> 02:13:29.334
- [ Laughing ]
- What? [ Laughs ]

02:13:29.418 --> 02:13:32.921
I knew the first time you blew that silly whistle.

02:13:34.423 --> 02:13:36.424
Oh, my love.

