- [ Maria ] ♪ With jam ♪
- [ Children ] ♪ A-B-C, A-B-C ♪

02:35:21.562 --> 02:35:24.940
- ♪ With jam ♪
- [ Children ] ♪ Do Re Mi, Do Re Mi ♪

