♪ The sun has gone to bed and so must I ♪

02:41:09.744 --> 02:41:19.502
♪ Good-bye ♪

02:41:19.587 --> 02:41:25.008
[ Von Trapp ]
♪ Good-bye ♪

02:41:25.092 --> 02:41:33.516
♪ Good-bye ♪♪

